NSMT-P 95590, holotype, 79.2 mm HL. (A–B) Scales from the dorsum below the interdorsal space; (C–D) from the top of the head between the parietal ridges. (A, C) Views from above; (B, D) oblique views. [Photos: N. Nakayama]
